==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: mèng mŭ sān qiān
===Etymology===
Literally: The mother of [[w:Mencius|Mencius]] changed her abode three times (to avoid bad influence on her son).
===Proverb===
# A wise mother would do everything for the healthy growth of her children.

